{"article_id":"dmYk75wbXpxUjVfj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Only three weeks away from a high-stakes meeting with mercurial North Korean leader Kim Jong-un ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"President Trump acknowledged Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that the odds","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"of their summit","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"taking place","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"as scheduled","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"are as uncertain as the flip of a commemorative coin .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Huddling with South Korean President Moon Jae-in","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"to strategize on the summit with Pyongyang ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Trump told reporters","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"that he is not sure","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"the denuclearization talks will go forward","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"as planned on June 12 in Singapore .","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"He hinted again","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"that China ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"which is engaged in contentious trade talks with the U.S. ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"may be undermining the North Korea summit .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"\" It may not work out for June 12th , \"","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"\" I don ' t want to waste a lot of time ,","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and I ' m sure","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"[ Mr. Kim ]","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"doesn ' t want to waste a lot of time .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"So there ' s a very substantial chance","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"that it won ' t work out . \"","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Asked by a reporter","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"if the fate of the summit is resting on a coin toss ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"the president replied ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"\" Yeah . \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"It was the most doubt","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"the president has expressed openly about the meeting","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"since North Korea threatened last week to back out .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"North Korea said","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"it won ' t agree to Mr. Trump ' s demand","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to give up its nuclear weapons unilaterally .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"A top South Korean official predicted this week","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that the summit was a \" 99.9 percent done deal . \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"The time frame for North Korean denuclearization also appears to be a sticking point .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"The U.S. and its allies South Korea and Japan are seeking immediate and verifiable removal of Pyongyang ' s weapons of mass destruction ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"while North Korea is reported to be asking for a longer timetable .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"\" All in one would be nice , \"","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"\" You do have some physical reasons","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that [ North Korea ] may not be able to do exactly that . \"","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Seeming to negotiate on camera ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"he is willing to accept Pyongyang ' s denuclearization over \" a very short period of time . \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"\" Essentially , that would be all in one , \"","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"\" There are certain conditions","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that we want ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"and I think","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"we ' ll get those conditions .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"if we don ' t ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"we don ' t have the meeting . \"","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo later told reporters","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that the Trump administration was still planning for a June 12 summit ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"although he wouldn ' t predict","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"whether it was certain .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"A North Korean flight","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"carrying international journalists","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"to cover the dismantlement of the Punggye-ri nuclear test ground","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"left Beijing for North Korea on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"without a group of South Korean reporters originally invited to attend .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"The nuclear test ground is scheduled to be dismantled sometime before Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"depending on weather conditions .","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"The president expressed hope for a summit with Mr. Kim at some point .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"the U.S. is emphasizing to Mr. Kim","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that an agreement will provide economic benefits to the isolated and heavily sanctioned North Korea .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"\" He will be extremely happy","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"if something works out , \"","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" He will be safe ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"he will be happy ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"his country will be rich ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"his country will be hardworking and very prosperous . \"","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"The prospect of eventual reunification between communist North Korea and democratic South Korea is also dangling over the summit .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Mr . Moon said","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" the fate and the future of the Korean Peninsula hinges on this . \"","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"\" I have every confidence","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that President Trump will be able to achieve a historic feat","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"of making the upcoming U.S.-North Korea summit successful","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and end the Korean War","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"that has been lasting for the past 65 years , \"","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Mr . Moon said .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"He also spoke of his hope","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that the U.S. will normalize relations with North Korea .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"North and South Korea have been separated by a Demilitarized Zone since a truce in 1953 .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Mr. Trump called it \" an artificial border \"","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"and spoke of the possibility","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"that the countries could \" go back to one Korea . \"","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"\" It ' s going to be largely up to them , as to whether or not they get together , \"","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"\" I would say","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that we are looking , certainly , right now , at two Koreas .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Two very successful Koreas .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"But someday in the future , maybe they ' ll get together","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and you ' ll go back to one Korea . \"","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"The president also was more direct Tuesday","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"in blaming Chinese President Xi Jinping ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"whom he calls a friend ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"for causing Mr. Kim ' s apparent change of heart about the summit .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"China is Pyongyang ' s main trading partner","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"and has largely worked with the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"to enforce economic sanctions on North Korea .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Mr. Kim has visited Beijing twice in two months ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"and his second trip to China on May 7 caught the U.S. by surprise .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"It came amid escalating threats of tariffs by China and the U.S.","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"as Mr. Trump seeks to stop what he calls China ' s unfair trade practices .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"\" The second meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"there was a little change in attitude from Kim Jong-un , \"","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"said Mr. Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"that he was disappointed by the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"\" The second time was like a surprise .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"I don ' t like that .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"things changed after that meeting .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"So I can ' t say","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"that I ' m happy about it .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"that President Xi is a world-class poker player . \"","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"Amid such high-level concerns and negotiations , the White House came under criticism for a decidedly more trivial aspect of the planned June 12 summit :","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"a commemorative \" challenge coin \"","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"marking the historic event .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"It features images of Mr. Trump and Mr. Kim ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"and is inscribed with the North Korean ' s title of \" supreme leader . \"","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Some critics on social media said","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"it was un-American to commemorate Mr. Kim ,","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"who has an abysmal human rights record .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer , New York Democrat , called on the White House to remove the image of a \" brutal dictator \" from the coin .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"\" I urge the White House to take Kim off the coin , \"","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Mr. Schumer said .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"\" Challenge coins are a time-honored tradition","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"and certainly appropriate in this situation ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"but Kim Jong-un ' s face has no place on this coin . \"","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"He suggested","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"that a more appropriate image would be the Peace House , a building in the Demilitarized Zone between North and South Korea .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"Such coins are released routinely","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"to commemorate a president ' s foreign trips .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders said","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"the coin \" is not something","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"that the White House has anything","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"to do with . \"","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"\" We don ' t have any input on the design , the manufacturer , the process , in any capacity , \"","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"\" This is a standard procedure by the White House Communications Agency ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"which is made up exclusively of career military officials .","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"And these coins are designed and done by that organization . \"","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"Coin or no coin ,","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"canceling the summit would be a blow to negotiations","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"Mr. Trump has hoped","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"would produce his biggest foreign policy achievement .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"As the preparations progressed","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"and North Korea released three American captives this month ,","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"there was even talk in some quarters","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"of awarding the president the Nobel Peace Prize","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"if the summit is fruitful .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"Mrs. Sanders said","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"the president ' s meeting with Mr . Moon was productive","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"and that the White House is still preparing for the summit","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"as scheduled .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"\" We ' re going to continue in preparations ,","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"and we ' ll see what happens , \"","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"Tensions between the U.S. and North Korea reached a crisis point last year","depth":3},{"id":170,"text":"as Pyongyang tested missiles","depth":5},{"id":171,"text":"believed capable of reaching the U.S. mainland","depth":5},{"id":172,"text":"and tested what was believed to be a hydrogen bomb .","depth":4},{"id":173,"text":"Mr. Trump threatened to bring \" fire and fury \" against North Korea","depth":4},{"id":174,"text":"if it struck the U.S.","depth":4},{"id":175,"text":"and ridiculed Mr. Kim as \" little rocket man . \"","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":351,"left":344,"right":350,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":344,"left":242,"right":343,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":235,"right":241,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":182,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":0,"right":181,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":181,"left":1,"right":180,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":180,"left":179,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":2,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":3,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":206,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":203,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":199,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":191,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":187,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":184,"right":186,"relation":"at